      src="http://via.placeholder.com/112x112"
      alt="Imagen de perfil de Adrian Alvarado"
    />

    <h1
      class="text-4xl/tight text-center text-balance font-black mb-6 text-neutral-1"
    >
      Hello, I'm Kartik, creative designer based in India.
